<br/>    80 feet that the wyrm can see must make a DC 21 
<br/>    Charisma save. On a failure, they are teleported to 
<br/>    the space where they were in the start of their turn. 
<br/>    In addition, they have disadvantage in their next 
<br/>    attack.
