>
> ***Greatsword.*** *Melee Weapon Attack:* +6 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 10 (2d6 + 3) slashing damage.
> 
> ***Void Strike (Recharge 5-6).***  The dragonspawn makes an strike that passes through all defenses against a target within 5 feet, causing them to take 38 (11d6) slashing damage on a failed DC 13 Dexterity save, or half as much damage on a successful one. This attack ignores resistance and immunity to slashing damage.

