> Among the infinite dragonspawns, the infinite chronomagi are those who have exceptional magic abilities. A chronomagus has the same statistics as an infinite dragonspawn, except it has a Charisma 16 and instead of Void Strike, it has the following trait:
>
> ***Innate Spellcasting.*** The chronomagus' innate spellcasting trait is Charisma (spell save DC 13). It can innately cast the following spells, requiring no material components:
