### Netherwing Dragon Lairs
[???.]

#### Lair Actions
On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the dragon takes a lair action to cause one of the following effects; the dragon cannot use the same effect two rounds in a row:
- Until initiative count 20 on the next round, the dragon can pass through solid walls, doors, ceilings, and floors as if the surfaces weren't there.

#### Regional Effects

