> ##### Variant: Nether Walker <!-- https://wc5e-cr-calculator.frogvall.com/?0;16;112;5;13;28;0;20;0;20;0;0;0;0;0;0;0;;;;;4;;;;;;;;;;3;;;;;;;;15;;;;;;;3;1;1;4;1;0;1;Shadow%20Bolt;Ray%20of%20Sickness;Hunger%20of%20Hadar -->
> Among the netherwing dragonspawns, the nether walkers are those who have exceptional magic abilities. A walker has the same statistics as an netherwing dragonspawn, except it has Charisma 16 and instead of Cleave, it has the following trait:
>
> ***Innate Spellcasting.*** The walker's innate spellcasting trait is Charisma (spell save DC 13, +5 to hit). It can innately cast the following spells, requiring no material components:
>
> <br/> At will: *dancing lights*, *mage hand*, ✦ *shadow bolt*, <br/>    *thaumaturgy*
> <br/> 3/day each: *faerie fire*, *ray of sickness*
> <br/> 2/day each: *darkness*, *invisibility*
> <br/> 1/day: *hunger of hadar*

